{
  "video_id": "d6NKdnZvdoo",
  "title": "Chrystia Freeland: The rise of the new global super-rich",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12629.0,
      "end_time": 17917.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s the most important economic fact of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17917.0,
      "end_time": 21947.0,
      "text": "We are living in an age of surging income inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21947.0,
      "end_time": 24872.0,
      "text": "particularly between those at the very top"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24872.0,
      "end_time": 26708.0,
      "text": "and everyone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26708.0,
      "end_time": 30730.0,
      "text": "This shift is the most striking in the U.S. and in the U.K.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30730.0,
      "end_time": 32928.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a global phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32928.0,
      "end_time": 35251.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s happening in communist China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35251.0,
      "end_time": 36974.0,
      "text": "in formerly communist Russia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36974.0,
      "end_time": 40268.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s happening in India, in my own native Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40268.0,
      "end_time": 43235.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re even seeing it in cozy social democracies"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43235.0,
      "end_time": 46860.0,
      "text": "like Sweden, Finland and Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46860.0,
      "end_time": 50771.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a few numbers to place what&#39;s happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50771.0,
      "end_time": 53480.0,
      "text": "In the 1970s, the One Percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53480.0,
      "end_time": 57757.0,
      "text": "accounted for about 10 percent of the national income"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57757.0,
      "end_time": 59521.0,
      "text": "in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59521.0,
      "end_time": 62830.0,
      "text": "Today, their share has more than doubled"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62830.0,
      "end_time": 65269.0,
      "text": "to above 20 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65269.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67369.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s even more striking"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67369.0,
      "end_time": 70055.0,
      "text": "is what&#39;s happening at the very tippy top"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70055.0,
      "end_time": 72297.0,
      "text": "of the income distribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72297.0,
      "end_time": 75301.0,
      "text": "The 0.1 percent in the U.S."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75301.0,
      "end_time": 78530.0,
      "text": "today account for more than eight percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78530.0,
      "end_time": 80420.0,
      "text": "of the national income."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80420.0,
      "end_time": 84913.0,
      "text": "They are where the One Percent was 30 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84913.0,
      "end_time": 87681.0,
      "text": "Let me give you another number to put that in perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 87681.0,
      "end_time": 91199.0,
      "text": "and this is a figure that was calculated in 2005"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91199.0,
      "end_time": 92658.0,
      "text": "by Robert Reich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92658.0,
      "end_time": 95397.0,
      "text": "the Secretary of Labor in the Clinton administration."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95397.0,
      "end_time": 100701.0,
      "text": "Reich took the wealth of two admittedly very rich men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100701.0,
      "end_time": 103421.0,
      "text": "Bill Gates and Warren Buffett,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103421.0,
      "end_time": 106370.0,
      "text": "and he found that it was equivalent to the wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106370.0,
      "end_time": 111123.0,
      "text": "of the bottom 40 percent of the U.S. population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111123.0,
      "end_time": 113965.0,
      "text": "120 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113965.0,
      "end_time": 116329.0,
      "text": "Now, as it happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116329.0,
      "end_time": 119133.0,
      "text": "Warren Buffett is not only himself a plutocrat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119133.0,
      "end_time": 122860.0,
      "text": "he is one of the most astute observers of that phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122860.0,
      "end_time": 126162.0,
      "text": "and he has his own favorite number."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126162.0,
      "end_time": 130105.0,
      "text": "Buffett likes to point out that in 1992,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130104.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132267.0,
      "text": "the combined wealth of the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132267.0,
      "end_time": 134596.0,
      "text": "on the Forbes 400 list --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134596.0,
      "end_time": 137993.0,
      "text": "and this is the list of the 400 richest Americans --"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137993.0,
      "end_time": 140765.0,
      "text": "was 300 billion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140765.0,
      "end_time": 141966.0,
      "text": "Just think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141966.0,
      "end_time": 143993.0,
      "text": "You didn&#39;t even need to be a billionaire"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143993.0,
      "end_time": 146966.0,
      "text": "to get on that list in 1992."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146966.0,
      "end_time": 150979.0,
      "text": "Well, today, that figure has more than quintupled"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150979.0,
      "end_time": 153865.0,
      "text": "to 1.7 trillion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153865.0,
      "end_time": 156043.0,
      "text": "and I probably don&#39;t need to tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156043.0,
      "end_time": 158504.0,
      "text": "that we haven&#39;t seen anything similar happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158504.0,
      "end_time": 159889.0,
      "text": "to the middle class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159889.0,
      "end_time": 164590.0,
      "text": "whose wealth has stagnated if not actually decreased."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164590.0,
      "end_time": 168650.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re living in the age of the global plutocracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168650.0,
      "end_time": 170691.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;ve been slow to notice it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170691.0,
      "end_time": 172374.0,
      "text": "One of the reasons, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 172374.0,
      "end_time": 175352.0,
      "text": "is a sort of boiled frog phenomenon."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 175352.0,
      "end_time": 177915.0,
      "text": "Changes which are slow and gradual"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 177915.0,
      "end_time": 179455.0,
      "text": "can be hard to notice"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 179455.0,
      "end_time": 182359.0,
      "text": "even if their ultimate impact is quite dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182359.0,
      "end_time": 185591.0,
      "text": "Think about what happened, after all, to the poor frog."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 185591.0,
      "end_time": 188406.0,
      "text": "But I think there&#39;s something else going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 188406.0,
      "end_time": 190516.0,
      "text": "Talking about income inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190516.0,
      "end_time": 193047.0,
      "text": "even if you&#39;re not on the Forbes 400 list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193047.0,
      "end_time": 195188.0,
      "text": "can make us feel uncomfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 195188.0,
      "end_time": 198633.0,
      "text": "It feels less positive, less optimistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198633.0,
      "end_time": 201162.0,
      "text": "to talk about how the pie is sliced"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201162.0,
      "end_time": 204214.0,
      "text": "than to think about how to make the pie bigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204214.0,
      "end_time": 206942.0,
      "text": "And if you do happen to be on the Forbes 400 list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206942.0,
      "end_time": 209740.0,
      "text": "talking about income distribution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209740.0,
      "end_time": 213427.0,
      "text": "and inevitably its cousin, income redistribution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213427.0,
      "end_time": 215967.0,
      "text": "can be downright threatening."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 215967.0,
      "end_time": 220243.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re living in the age of surging income inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 220243.0,
      "end_time": 222356.0,
      "text": "especially at the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222356.0,
      "end_time": 225944.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s driving it, and what can we do about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225944.0,
      "end_time": 229610.0,
      "text": "One set of causes is political:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 229610.0,
      "end_time": 235205.0,
      "text": "lower taxes, deregulation, particularly of financial services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 235205.0,
      "end_time": 240335.0,
      "text": "privatization, weaker legal protections for trade unions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240335.0,
      "end_time": 242775.0,
      "text": "all of these have contributed"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242775.0,
      "end_time": 246892.0,
      "text": "to more and more income going to the very, very top."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 246892.0,
      "end_time": 250315.0,
      "text": "A lot of these political factors can be broadly lumped"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 250315.0,
      "end_time": 253644.0,
      "text": "under the category of &quot;crony capitalism,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 253644.0,
      "end_time": 255821.0,
      "text": "political changes that benefit a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 255821.0,
      "end_time": 257983.0,
      "text": "of well-connected insiders"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257983.0,
      "end_time": 261521.0,
      "text": "but don&#39;t actually do much good for the rest of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261521.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264910.0,
      "text": "In practice, getting rid of crony capitalism"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 264910.0,
      "end_time": 266951.0,
      "text": "is incredibly difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266951.0,
      "end_time": 270444.0,
      "text": "Think of all the years reformers of various stripes"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 270444.0,
      "end_time": 273838.0,
      "text": "have tried to get rid of corruption in Russia, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 273838.0,
      "end_time": 276867.0,
      "text": "or how hard it is to re-regulate the banks"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276867.0,
      "end_time": 280024.0,
      "text": "even after the most profound financial crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 280024.0,
      "end_time": 281646.0,
      "text": "since the Great Depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 281646.0,
      "end_time": 286242.0,
      "text": "or even how difficult it is to get the big multinational companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 286242.0,
      "end_time": 290253.0,
      "text": "including those whose motto might be &quot;don&#39;t do evil,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 290253.0,
      "end_time": 293027.0,
      "text": "to pay taxes at a rate even approaching that"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293027.0,
      "end_time": 295135.0,
      "text": "paid by the middle class."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 295135.0,
      "end_time": 298171.0,
      "text": "But while getting rid of crony capitalism in practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 298171.0,
      "end_time": 300167.0,
      "text": "is really, really hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 300167.0,
      "end_time": 303635.0,
      "text": "at least intellectually, it&#39;s an easy problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 303635.0,
      "end_time": 309284.0,
      "text": "After all, no one is actually in favor of crony capitalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309284.0,
      "end_time": 311931.0,
      "text": "Indeed, this is one of those rare issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 311931.0,
      "end_time": 315166.0,
      "text": "that unites the left and the right."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315166.0,
      "end_time": 317986.0,
      "text": "A critique of crony capitalism is as central"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 317986.0,
      "end_time": 322283.0,
      "text": "to the Tea Party as it is to Occupy Wall Street."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 322283.0,
      "end_time": 326621.0,
      "text": "But if crony capitalism is, intellectually at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 326621.0,
      "end_time": 328656.0,
      "text": "the easy part of the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 328656.0,
      "end_time": 331931.0,
      "text": "things get trickier when you look at the economic drivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331931.0,
      "end_time": 334684.0,
      "text": "of surging income inequality."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 334684.0,
      "end_time": 338423.0,
      "text": "In and of themselves, these aren&#39;t too mysterious."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338423.0,
      "end_time": 341470.0,
      "text": "Globalization and the technology revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341470.0,
      "end_time": 344010.0,
      "text": "the twin economic transformations"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 344010.0,
      "end_time": 345708.0,
      "text": "which are changing our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 345708.0,
      "end_time": 347805.0,
      "text": "and transforming the global economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 347805.0,
      "end_time": 351272.0,
      "text": "are also powering the rise of the super-rich."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 351272.0,
      "end_time": 352852.0,
      "text": "Just think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 352852.0,
      "end_time": 354840.0,
      "text": "For the first time in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 354840.0,
      "end_time": 357579.0,
      "text": "if you are an energetic entrepreneur"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357579.0,
      "end_time": 359278.0,
      "text": "with a brilliant new idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 359278.0,
      "end_time": 361693.0,
      "text": "or a fantastic new product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 361693.0,
      "end_time": 365372.0,
      "text": "you have almost instant, almost frictionless access"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 365372.0,
      "end_time": 369352.0,
      "text": "to a global market of more than a billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 369352.0,
      "end_time": 373186.0,
      "text": "As a result, if you are very, very smart"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 373186.0,
      "end_time": 374981.0,
      "text": "and very, very lucky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 374981.0,
      "end_time": 377832.0,
      "text": "you can get very, very rich"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 377832.0,
      "end_time": 380362.0,
      "text": "very, very quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 380362.0,
      "end_time": 383204.0,
      "text": "The latest poster boy for this phenomenon"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 383204.0,
      "end_time": 385184.0,
      "text": "is David Karp."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 385184.0,
      "end_time": 388039.0,
      "text": "The 26-year-old founder of Tumblr"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 388039.0,
      "end_time": 390821.0,
      "text": "recently sold his company to Yahoo"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 390821.0,
      "end_time": 393854.0,
      "text": "for 1.1 billion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 393854.0,
      "end_time": 395392.0,
      "text": "Think about that for a minute:"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 395392.0,
      "end_time": 399806.0,
      "text": "1.1 billion dollars, 26 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 399806.0,
      "end_time": 403253.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easiest to see how the technology revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 403253.0,
      "end_time": 406874.0,
      "text": "and globalization are creating this sort of superstar effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 406874.0,
      "end_time": 408817.0,
      "text": "in highly visible fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 408817.0,
      "end_time": 411120.0,
      "text": "like sports and entertainment."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 411120.0,
      "end_time": 414495.0,
      "text": "We can all watch how a fantastic athlete"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 414495.0,
      "end_time": 418839.0,
      "text": "or a fantastic performer can today leverage his or her skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 418839.0,
      "end_time": 422507.0,
      "text": "across the global economy as never before."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 422507.0,
      "end_time": 424587.0,
      "text": "But today, that superstar effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 424587.0,
      "end_time": 427569.0,
      "text": "is happening across the entire economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 427569.0,
      "end_time": 429746.0,
      "text": "We have superstar technologists."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 429746.0,
      "end_time": 431467.0,
      "text": "We have superstar bankers."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 431467.0,
      "end_time": 434803.0,
      "text": "We have superstar lawyers and superstar architects."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 434803.0,
      "end_time": 436232.0,
      "text": "There are superstar cooks"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 436232.0,
      "end_time": 437744.0,
      "text": "and superstar farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 437744.0,
      "end_time": 440527.0,
      "text": "There are even, and this is my personal favorite example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 440527.0,
      "end_time": 442518.0,
      "text": "superstar dentists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442518.0,
      "end_time": 444622.0,
      "text": "the most dazzling exemplar of whom"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 444622.0,
      "end_time": 447984.0,
      "text": "is Bernard Touati, the Frenchman who ministers"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 447984.0,
      "end_time": 450303.0,
      "text": "to the smiles of fellow superstars"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 450303.0,
      "end_time": 452984.0,
      "text": "like Russian oligarch Roman Abramovich"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 452984.0,
      "end_time": 455845.0,
      "text": "or European-born American fashion designer"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 455845.0,
      "end_time": 457890.0,
      "text": "Diane von Furstenberg."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457890.0,
      "end_time": 460973.0,
      "text": "But while it&#39;s pretty easy to see how globalization"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460973.0,
      "end_time": 462885.0,
      "text": "and the technology revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 462885.0,
      "end_time": 465356.0,
      "text": "are creating this global plutocracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 465356.0,
      "end_time": 469523.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s a lot harder is figuring out what to think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 469523.0,
      "end_time": 471049.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 471049.0,
      "end_time": 473426.0,
      "text": "in contrast with crony capitalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473426.0,
      "end_time": 477336.0,
      "text": "so much of what globalization and the technology revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 477336.0,
      "end_time": 479699.0,
      "text": "have done is highly positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 479699.0,
      "end_time": 481434.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 481434.0,
      "end_time": 485044.0,
      "text": "I love the Internet. I love my mobile devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 485044.0,
      "end_time": 486878.0,
      "text": "I love the fact that they mean that"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 486878.0,
      "end_time": 490564.0,
      "text": "whoever chooses to will be able to watch this talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 490564.0,
      "end_time": 492611.0,
      "text": "far beyond this auditorium."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 492611.0,
      "end_time": 495720.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m even more of a fan of globalization."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 495720.0,
      "end_time": 497707.0,
      "text": "This is the transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 497707.0,
      "end_time": 500131.0,
      "text": "which has lifted hundreds of millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 500131.0,
      "end_time": 503180.0,
      "text": "of the world&#39;s poorest people out of poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503180.0,
      "end_time": 504622.0,
      "text": "and into the middle class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 504622.0,
      "end_time": 507664.0,
      "text": "and if you happen to live in the rich part of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507664.0,
      "end_time": 511171.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s made many new products affordable --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 511171.0,
      "end_time": 513697.0,
      "text": "who do you think built your iPhone? —"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 513697.0,
      "end_time": 517519.0,
      "text": "and things that we&#39;ve relied on for a long time much cheaper."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 517519.0,
      "end_time": 520143.0,
      "text": "Think of your dishwasher or your t-shirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 520143.0,
      "end_time": 522679.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s not to like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 522679.0,
      "end_time": 524571.0,
      "text": "Well, a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 524571.0,
      "end_time": 526675.0,
      "text": "One of the things that worries me"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 526675.0,
      "end_time": 530838.0,
      "text": "is how easily what you might call meritocratic plutocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 530838.0,
      "end_time": 533534.0,
      "text": "can become crony plutocracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 533534.0,
      "end_time": 536193.0,
      "text": "Imagine you&#39;re a brilliant entrepreneur"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 536193.0,
      "end_time": 539570.0,
      "text": "who has successfully sold that idea or that product"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 539570.0,
      "end_time": 540949.0,
      "text": "to the global billions"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 540949.0,
      "end_time": 543515.0,
      "text": "and become a billionaire in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 543515.0,
      "end_time": 545884.0,
      "text": "It gets tempting at that point"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 545884.0,
      "end_time": 548859.0,
      "text": "to use your economic nous"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 548859.0,
      "end_time": 553131.0,
      "text": "to manipulate the rules of the global political economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 553131.0,
      "end_time": 555217.0,
      "text": "in your own favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 555217.0,
      "end_time": 557966.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s no mere hypothetical example."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 557966.0,
      "end_time": 562395.0,
      "text": "Think about Amazon, Apple, Google, Starbucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 562395.0,
      "end_time": 564499.0,
      "text": "These are among the world&#39;s most admired,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 564499.0,
      "end_time": 567045.0,
      "text": "most beloved, most innovative companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 567045.0,
      "end_time": 569969.0,
      "text": "They also happen to be particularly adept"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 569969.0,
      "end_time": 572207.0,
      "text": "at working the international tax system"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 572207.0,
      "end_time": 576765.0,
      "text": "so as to lower their tax bill very, very significantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 576765.0,
      "end_time": 581080.0,
      "text": "And why stop at just playing the global political"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 581080.0,
      "end_time": 583168.0,
      "text": "and economic system as it exists"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 583168.0,
      "end_time": 585313.0,
      "text": "to your own maximum advantage?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 585313.0,
      "end_time": 589630.0,
      "text": "Once you have the tremendous economic power"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 589630.0,
      "end_time": 592703.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re seeing at the very, very top of the income distribution"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 592703.0,
      "end_time": 595953.0,
      "text": "and the political power that inevitably entails,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 595953.0,
      "end_time": 598466.0,
      "text": "it becomes tempting as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 598466.0,
      "end_time": 602054.0,
      "text": "to start trying to change the rules of the game"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 602054.0,
      "end_time": 604156.0,
      "text": "in your own favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 604156.0,
      "end_time": 606890.0,
      "text": "Again, this is no mere hypothetical."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 606890.0,
      "end_time": 608825.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what the Russian oligarchs did"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 608825.0,
      "end_time": 612087.0,
      "text": "in creating the sale-of-the-century privatization"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 612087.0,
      "end_time": 614057.0,
      "text": "of Russia&#39;s natural resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 614057.0,
      "end_time": 615831.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s one way of describing what happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 615831.0,
      "end_time": 617866.0,
      "text": "with deregulation of the financial services"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 617866.0,
      "end_time": 620101.0,
      "text": "in the U.S. and the U.K."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 620101.0,
      "end_time": 622027.0,
      "text": "A second thing that worries me"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 622027.0,
      "end_time": 624758.0,
      "text": "is how easily meritocratic plutocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 624758.0,
      "end_time": 627504.0,
      "text": "can become aristocracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 627504.0,
      "end_time": 629579.0,
      "text": "One way of describing the plutocrats"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 629579.0,
      "end_time": 631386.0,
      "text": "is as alpha geeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 631386.0,
      "end_time": 633900.0,
      "text": "and they are people who are acutely aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 633900.0,
      "end_time": 636308.0,
      "text": "of how important highly sophisticated"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 636308.0,
      "end_time": 640490.0,
      "text": "analytical and quantitative skills are in today&#39;s economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 640490.0,
      "end_time": 642909.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s why they are spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 642909.0,
      "end_time": 645686.0,
      "text": "unprecedented time and resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 645686.0,
      "end_time": 647583.0,
      "text": "educating their own children."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 647583.0,
      "end_time": 650850.0,
      "text": "The middle class is spending more on schooling too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 650850.0,
      "end_time": 653211.0,
      "text": "but in the global educational arms race"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 653211.0,
      "end_time": 654995.0,
      "text": "that starts at nursery school"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 654995.0,
      "end_time": 658733.0,
      "text": "and ends at Harvard, Stanford or MIT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 658733.0,
      "end_time": 662211.0,
      "text": "the 99 percent is increasingly outgunned"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 662211.0,
      "end_time": 663750.0,
      "text": "by the One Percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 663750.0,
      "end_time": 666456.0,
      "text": "The result is something that economists Alan Krueger"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 666456.0,
      "end_time": 670161.0,
      "text": "and Miles Corak call the Great Gatsby Curve."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 670161.0,
      "end_time": 672964.0,
      "text": "As income inequality increases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 672964.0,
      "end_time": 675737.0,
      "text": "social mobility decreases."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 675737.0,
      "end_time": 678495.0,
      "text": "The plutocracy may be a meritocracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 678495.0,
      "end_time": 680711.0,
      "text": "but increasingly you have to be born"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 680711.0,
      "end_time": 685595.0,
      "text": "on the top rung of the ladder to even take part in that race."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 685595.0,
      "end_time": 688619.0,
      "text": "The third thing, and this is what worries me the most,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 688619.0,
      "end_time": 692970.0,
      "text": "is the extent to which those same largely positive forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 692970.0,
      "end_time": 696160.0,
      "text": "which are driving the rise of the global plutocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 696160.0,
      "end_time": 699592.0,
      "text": "also happen to be hollowing out the middle class"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 699592.0,
      "end_time": 702546.0,
      "text": "in Western industrialized economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 702546.0,
      "end_time": 704633.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 704633.0,
      "end_time": 707706.0,
      "text": "Those same forces that are creating billionaires"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 707706.0,
      "end_time": 711729.0,
      "text": "are also devouring many traditional middle-class jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 711729.0,
      "end_time": 714668.0,
      "text": "When&#39;s the last time you used a travel agent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 714668.0,
      "end_time": 717749.0,
      "text": "And in contrast with the industrial revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 717749.0,
      "end_time": 719905.0,
      "text": "the titans of our new economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 719905.0,
      "end_time": 722707.0,
      "text": "aren&#39;t creating that many new jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 722707.0,
      "end_time": 726526.0,
      "text": "At its zenith, G.M. employed hundreds of thousands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 726526.0,
      "end_time": 729549.0,
      "text": "Facebook fewer than 10,000."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 729549.0,
      "end_time": 732219.0,
      "text": "The same is true of globalization."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 732219.0,
      "end_time": 735462.0,
      "text": "For all that it is raising hundreds of millions of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 735462.0,
      "end_time": 737802.0,
      "text": "out of poverty in the emerging markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 737802.0,
      "end_time": 740668.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also outsourcing a lot of jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 740668.0,
      "end_time": 742969.0,
      "text": "from the developed Western economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 742969.0,
      "end_time": 745736.0,
      "text": "The terrifying reality is"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 745736.0,
      "end_time": 747993.0,
      "text": "that there is no economic rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 747993.0,
      "end_time": 750930.0,
      "text": "which automatically translates"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 750930.0,
      "end_time": 752633.0,
      "text": "increased economic growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 752633.0,
      "end_time": 754943.0,
      "text": "into widely shared prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 754943.0,
      "end_time": 757617.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s shown in what I consider to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 757617.0,
      "end_time": 761300.0,
      "text": "the most scary economic statistic of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 761300.0,
      "end_time": 765358.0,
      "text": "Since the late 1990s, increases in productivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 765358.0,
      "end_time": 768036.0,
      "text": "have been decoupled from increases"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 768036.0,
      "end_time": 769970.0,
      "text": "in wages and employment."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 769970.0,
      "end_time": 772914.0,
      "text": "That means that our countries are getting richer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 772914.0,
      "end_time": 775538.0,
      "text": "our companies are getting more efficient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 775538.0,
      "end_time": 777479.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;re not creating more jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 777479.0,
      "end_time": 781350.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re not paying people, as a whole, more."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 781350.0,
      "end_time": 785559.0,
      "text": "One scary conclusion you could draw from all of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 785559.0,
      "end_time": 789270.0,
      "text": "is to worry about structural unemployment."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 789270.0,
      "end_time": 793057.0,
      "text": "What worries me more is a different nightmare scenario."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 793057.0,
      "end_time": 795649.0,
      "text": "After all, in a totally free labor market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 795649.0,
      "end_time": 798851.0,
      "text": "we could find jobs for pretty much everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 798851.0,
      "end_time": 800879.0,
      "text": "The dystopia that worries me"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 800879.0,
      "end_time": 804525.0,
      "text": "is a universe in which a few geniuses"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 804525.0,
      "end_time": 806605.0,
      "text": "invent Google and its ilk"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 806605.0,
      "end_time": 811800.0,
      "text": "and the rest of us are employed giving them massages."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 811800.0,
      "end_time": 814433.0,
      "text": "So when I get really depressed about all of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 814433.0,
      "end_time": 818262.0,
      "text": "I comfort myself in thinking about the Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 818262.0,
      "end_time": 822157.0,
      "text": "After all, for all its grim, satanic mills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 822157.0,
      "end_time": 824657.0,
      "text": "it worked out pretty well, didn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 824657.0,
      "end_time": 831680.0,
      "text": "After all, all of us here are richer, healthier, taller --"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 831680.0,
      "end_time": 833706.0,
      "text": "well, there are a few exceptions —"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 833706.0,
      "end_time": 838697.0,
      "text": "and live longer than our ancestors in the early 19th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 838697.0,
      "end_time": 841281.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s important to remember"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 841281.0,
      "end_time": 844103.0,
      "text": "that before we learned how to share the fruits"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 844103.0,
      "end_time": 845782.0,
      "text": "of the Industrial Revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 845782.0,
      "end_time": 848345.0,
      "text": "with the broad swathes of society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 848345.0,
      "end_time": 851740.0,
      "text": "we had to go through two depressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 851740.0,
      "end_time": 853599.0,
      "text": "the Great Depression of the 1930s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 853599.0,
      "end_time": 856453.0,
      "text": "the Long Depression of the 1870s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 856453.0,
      "end_time": 859620.0,
      "text": "two world wars, communist revolutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 859620.0,
      "end_time": 861699.0,
      "text": "in Russia and in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 861699.0,
      "end_time": 864024.0,
      "text": "and an era of tremendous social"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 864024.0,
      "end_time": 866780.0,
      "text": "and political upheaval in the West."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 866780.0,
      "end_time": 869500.0,
      "text": "We also, not coincidentally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 869500.0,
      "end_time": 872038.0,
      "text": "went through an era of tremendous"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 872038.0,
      "end_time": 874617.0,
      "text": "social and political inventions."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 874617.0,
      "end_time": 876961.0,
      "text": "We created the modern welfare state."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 876961.0,
      "end_time": 878703.0,
      "text": "We created public education."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 878703.0,
      "end_time": 880407.0,
      "text": "We created public health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 880407.0,
      "end_time": 882182.0,
      "text": "We created public pensions."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 882182.0,
      "end_time": 884207.0,
      "text": "We created unions."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 884207.0,
      "end_time": 886723.0,
      "text": "Today, we are living through an era"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 886723.0,
      "end_time": 888684.0,
      "text": "of economic transformation"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 888684.0,
      "end_time": 891990.0,
      "text": "comparable in its scale and its scope"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 891990.0,
      "end_time": 894258.0,
      "text": "to the Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 894258.0,
      "end_time": 897449.0,
      "text": "To be sure that this new economy benefits us all"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 897449.0,
      "end_time": 899567.0,
      "text": "and not just the plutocrats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 899567.0,
      "end_time": 901231.0,
      "text": "we need to embark on an era"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 901231.0,
      "end_time": 905150.0,
      "text": "of comparably ambitious social and political change."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 905150.0,
      "end_time": 907808.0,
      "text": "We need a new New Deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 907808.0,
      "end_time": 917808.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}